&kp LA(LC(LS(LEFT)))  &kp LG(LEFT)      &mo 10             &kp LG(RIGHT)      &kp LS(LA(LC(RIGHT)))  &kp T       &none      &kp LC(A)   &kp LEFT         &kp DOWN   &kp RIGHT    &kp LG(Q)
